{"tid":665112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖 圈子朋友VS圈外朋友","createTime":"2018-05-14T16:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T02:25:28.000Z","uid":162209,"like":0,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f67f73000d8367f6e42cf960cc9d4c456daf718f","tid":665112,"uid":162209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"拍拖你地會揀圈子（身邊同一堆fd）入便既人<br />\n<br />\n定係<br />\n<br />\n圈外（本來同圈內朋友無咩common fd）既人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圈內朋友會唸如果萬一真係分手點算，成個圈子咪好尷尬，例如本身3-4個fd底（有男有女），會連本身既關係圈都影響左<br />\n<br />\n圈外朋友，就好似無咩壓力，一齊/散左都無咩影響，介紹俾朋友識又唔會話埋堆玩，所以相對就無咩壓力<br />\n<br />\n你地會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮 圈內朋友<br />\n負皮 圈外朋友"},{"pid":"132e2736ff3a81b0a1adf1fa80bd8645a5664380","tid":665112,"uid":84908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"梗係圈外 食完即換另一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c5b1812f895982300119aa522472032431012a","tid":665112,"uid":2959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"圈內先on9 飯局個啲都要一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b865db4eebb823b8b48493c53dbfc67586f57c","tid":665112,"uid":107149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"但圈外又唔知佢啲朋友咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d103af38e5e639fb8ed6f28bdf8c412c201d11","tid":665112,"uid":176427,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"而家有得你揀咩"},{"pid":"0123bf37a137fb34e157d512239d34faff75c95e","tid":665112,"uid":162209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98c5b1812f895982300119aa522472032431012a","tid":665112,"uid":2959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"圈內先on9 飯局個啲都要一齊<img src=\"/asse